Title: Torero
Actors: Luis Procuna, Consuelo Procuna, Ángel Procuna, Antonio Sevilia
Plot: The life of the famed Mexican bullfighter Luis Procuna, from his boyhood through his training and the triumphs that followed as Procuna rose to the peak of his profession.
Awards: Nominated for 1 Oscar. Another 3 wins & 1 nomination.
